Detailed Description

template<class T, class Metric>
struct CoverTree< T, Metric >::LinkData::Compare

Comparator that compares LinkData objects by the level of each one's current Node.

The current node at the front of a priority queue using this comparator will have the highest level among all nodes in the priority queue.
